<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Thousand-fold" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Thousand-fold,</orth> multiplied by a thousand: <cit><quote>brings a t. more care,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a t. it doth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.5.46" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 46</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a t. more bitter,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>but more in Troilus t. I see,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.310" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 310</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>